Got it. Since you've followed the instructions and the accounts are still not displaying any spend, let's double-check a few things. Make sure that the postback URL is correctly set up in Redtrack and that it's properly linked to your NewsBreak campaigns. You can refer to this guide for detailed steps: [How to set up a RedTrack Postback on NewsBreak](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/25515090832013-How-to-set-up-a-RedTrack-Postback-on-NewsBreak). If everything looks good on your end, it might be an issue with data synchronization or tracking discrepancies. In that case, I recommend reaching out to Redtrack support for further investigation.
